{"tid":358663,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[求職]殯儀入行一問","createTime":"2017-08-14T00:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T07:47:29.000Z","uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7cdd45bc51062dcbe0c344a05a11929b27df43c","tid":358663,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T00:12:22.000Z","msg":"如題，記得之前有個類似嘅Post，不過唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟兩個月前祼辭咗，打散工，覺得唔係好穩定，又想入啲特別啲嘅行業，想問以下幾樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n1.最簡單，都最頭痕嘅，點入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就咁行去門口問佢請唔請人咁得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係勞工處有招聘?<br />\n<br />\n2.工作時間大概幾點到幾點?人工大概幾多?<br />\n<br />\n3需要有咩學歷、工作經驗?我做咗六年製作，會考0分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.可唔可以留長頭髮?不過唔得都冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n5.好撚爛口，但當然唔會出聲講啲先人，有冇特別影響?<br />\n<br />\n6.有帶開兩條佛珠，驚唔驚得罪老友?<br />\n<br />\n7.靈異少少，俾老友搞過一年，驚唔驚唔好腳頭?不過我唔怕嘅。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我唔係諗住玩玩下，認真想入行嘅，希望有師兄解答同埋成全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7635e15292220d92163f38db9eb53b6af8f876c","tid":358663,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a66499b85ffbba46d7cffda8c72f7fb62579c7","tid":358663,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:11:53.000Z","msg":"劉明學野"},{"pid":"97bb99f5ca7c2c233581aac09385ac51176c6d08","tid":358663,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:27:27.000Z","msg":"lm學野 x2"},{"pid":"68cdef7e753b5a79f937004b21a55549a1a3fb70","tid":358663,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:30:41.000Z","msg":"你fb 搵賣棺材的男孩<br />\n記得佢話可以逐家問請唔請人"},{"pid":"880af64fb4e8200ba5fc4c9d064768a8b857c9ff","tid":358663,"uid":55426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"報紙成日都有登請人 得閒留意下"},{"pid":"b91959279bc5eeea07f8039cca3853f4fc51c2d7","tid":358663,"uid":16150,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"1. 多數唔識行內人可以唔洗入行<br />\n<br />\n2. 因為真係好好搵，所以多數會留畀自己熟人做，不過你都可以試下逐家問<br />\n<br />\n3. 學歷冇所謂，都唔知有咩科關殯儀事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唯一條件係要有陰陽眼<br />\n<br />\n利申：殯儀朋友講嘅<br />\n<br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e81a4dba40ce42e69ce7a33fdc8801017f2787","tid":358663,"uid":19485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"我只係知，呢行係接近無假放，星期日都會有唔同既call搵你<br />\n基本要返6日，時間應該唔同位唔同掛<br />\n同某啲職位要跟師父，師父去決定係有無得繼續做<br />\n<br />\n屋企有兩個屋企人做緊呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩個唔同職位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6天工作係基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9760949eb18f70909ac09b4eaab901d7e896e6ea","tid":358663,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你fb 搵賣棺材的男孩<br />\n記得佢話可以逐家問請唔請人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046ffdeb90dcf74b963bc758ec9c1ef82979614a","tid":358663,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我只係知，呢行係接近無假放，星期日都會有唔同既call搵你<br />\n基本要返6日，時間應該唔同位唔同掛<br />\n同某啲職位要跟師父，師父去決定係有無得繼續做<br />\n<br />\n屋企有兩個屋企人做緊呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩個唔同職位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6天工作係基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma